title: why
pid: 3ed86130-f100-4785-b87e-b7960a62903c
body: |2-
  "Like" and "dislike" might already be specific enough.
  But even if more detail is important enough to be worth
  the complexity cost to the user,
  there is still value in aggregating different peoples' partitions of 'what I like'
  into a collective 'like' statistic.
